description: Winter has been too long, that I had to wear the jacket, scarf and all the other stuff. Looking forward to have an opportunity to just take off my pant or shorts and fuck some young cuties outside, in the park, forrest or just wherever. I´ve met two youngsters walking the street. One of them didn´t like my little project at all. Even went angry and told me to fuck off. Well, whatever. I focused on the other one. He was talkative, nice and very fun to chat with. Did even a little bit of pole dancing for me, right there on the street. Once I started with money, I could see the golden bars in his eyes. Once I got the prize right, it was just a matter of choice to choose where I´ll fuck him. In this shitty weather we didn´t have that much choice. Luckily, there was a small garage...
title: Czech Hunter 182
